86
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:34,450
That's right.

87
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:36,200
Can you describe

88
00:08:36,210 --> 00:08:37,740
the entire situation to me?

89
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:42,030
Back then, I was terrified.

90
00:08:42,740 --> 00:08:45,080
