141
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:31,940
Did you steal my keys again?

142
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,850
Do you expect me to wait for you

143
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:35,250
in front of the door then?

144
00:10:54,690 --> 00:10:56,830
Were you hurt?

145
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,680
Lowly thugs like them

146
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,020
can never hurt me.

147
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,680
I'm glad to hear that.

148
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,380
Where did you go after that?

149
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:05,780
I went back to the mall
to retrieve my stuff.

150
00:11:07,290 --> 00:11:08,290
This is a warning.

151
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,560
You better pick an appropriate time

152
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,420
if you plan to summon me next time.

153
00:11:12,660 --> 00:11:13,670
