154
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:14,550
if I lose them.

155
00:11:15,140 --> 00:11:16,530
Did you rob a bank?

156
00:11:20,050 --> 00:11:22,150
Are you sure you only pawned
your jade pendant

157
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,080
and didn't rob a bank?

158
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,350
Although I don't mind

159
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,980
messing with the cops here,

160
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:28,330
I won't attract their attention

161
00:11:28,330 --> 00:11:29,460
under such circumstances

162
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:30,850
unless it's necessary.

163
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,230
After all,

164
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:32,860
I don't have

165
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:34,330
a legal identity in this era yet.

166
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:36,330
Great. You had me for a moment there.

167
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:38,110
If so...

168
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:38,950
Are you trying

169
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:40,250
to ask me why I appeared

170
00:11:40,420 --> 00:11:41,640
and saved you again?

171
00:11:43,450 --> 00:11:44,780
Let me be clear with you.

172
00:11:45,130 --> 00:11:46,640
I wasn't trying to save you.

173
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:49,160
I was just keeping an eye on my hostage.

174
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,460
Besides,

175
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:52,640
when it comes to double-crossing people,

176
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,900
I'm the only one

177
00:11:54,070 --> 00:11:56,070
who can double-cross other people.

178
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:57,470
So, it was me

179
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,070
who summoned you again?

180
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,920
I remember I told you this before.

181
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:02,680
I heard your voice

182
00:12:02,850 --> 00:12:04,070
before I was summoned by you.

183
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:06,420
[Someone, help me.
Stop showing off your relationship.]

184
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:08,060
[Can someone help me out?]

185
00:12:08,810 --> 00:12:11,000
[Help!]

186
00:12:12,170 --> 00:12:14,100
I heard your voice again this time.

187
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:17,260
But what's the connection
between the two incidents?

188
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:18,790
Although the words you said

189
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:21,200
weren't related,

190
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:23,300
both situations

191
00:12:23,430 --> 00:12:24,630
were pretty similar.

192
00:12:26,410 --> 00:12:27,630
It happens

193
00:12:28,010 --> 00:12:29,480
whenever you need a hero

194
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,860
to save you.

195
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:32,880
A hero?

196
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,070
You don't say?

197
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:37,040
Do you think you can escape unscathed

198
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:37,920
in both situations

199
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,050
without any help?

200
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:42,750
[He's the person]

201
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:44,480
[the fairy had sent to save me.]

202
00:12:45,350 --> 00:12:45,900
[If so, that means]

203
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:48,100
[I can do whatever I want in the future.]

204
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,470
[I just need to summon him]

205
00:12:49,470 --> 00:12:51,110
[during crucial moments.]

206
00:12:54,090 --> 00:12:54,950
Let me warn you.

207
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:56,230
You're not allowed

208
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,460
to get into any trouble in the future.

209
00:12:58,670 --> 00:13:00,390
What trouble can I get into?

210
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,690
With a brain like yours,

211
00:13:01,690 --> 00:13:02,450
I wouldn't be surprised

212
00:13:02,450 --> 00:13:03,780
if you get into trouble.

213
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,590
Anyway, I've made myself clear.

214
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,070
If you summon me again,

215
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:08,030
I will never help you out

216
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,690
no matter what happens to you.

217
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:10,760
And, if you keep

218
00:13:10,890 --> 00:13:12,230
getting into trouble,

219
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,220
I have no choice

220
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:15,880
