224
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:28,320
Cut to the chase.

225
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:31,480
I will definitely regret this.

226
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:34,160
Come with me.

227
00:13:39,990 --> 00:13:40,460
Come on.

228
00:14:00,610 --> 00:14:01,410
Come in.

229
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:09,520
