235
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,120
But only

236
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,170
if you agree to one condition.

237
00:14:23,170 --> 00:14:24,930
What condition?

238
00:14:27,370 --> 00:14:28,080
You cannot

239
00:14:28,290 --> 00:14:29,720
come to find me whenever you like it,

240
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,380
especially

241
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:31,830
when my mother is around.

242
00:14:31,860 --> 00:14:32,870
If not, I won't be able to explain myself

243
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:34,330
when she sees us together.

244
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,920
Are you saying

245
00:14:39,090 --> 00:14:41,060
that I need to consider your feelings

246
00:14:41,060 --> 00:14:42,990
and not create any trouble for you?

247
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:44,380
That's right.

248
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:53,070
But why must I

249
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,640
consider your feelings?

250
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,510
You!

251
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:57,290
Did you forget your status?

252
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,120
You're a hostage.

253
00:14:59,450 --> 00:15:01,550
I'm the one who's keeping you hostage.

254
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:03,880
You don't want your mother
to see me? Fine.

255
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:05,920
You have to give me something in return.

256
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:06,930
You're

257
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:09,200
rotten to the core.

258
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:12,730
You don't like it?

259
00:15:12,730 --> 00:15:14,730
I can move back to your unit anytime.

260
00:15:15,040 --> 00:15:16,930
Your bed is pretty comfortable anyway.

261
00:15:16,930 --> 00:15:17,980
Wait a minute!

262
00:15:19,610 --> 00:15:21,210
Tell me then.

263
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:22,390
What do you want?

264
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,410
I need

265
00:15:25,490 --> 00:15:26,710
a smartphone.

266
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:29,540
