267
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:32,300
A smartphone

268
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:34,400
is just like a personal computer.

269
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:36,290
It has an independent operating space

270
00:15:36,290 --> 00:15:37,510
and its own programs.

271
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,520
Its user can install

272
00:15:39,650 --> 00:15:41,500
software, games, navigation apps,

273
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:42,550
and all kinds of programs offered by

274
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:43,430
third-party service providers.

275
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:45,290
It's a collective term for phones

276
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,790
that can connect to
the Internet wirelessly

277
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:48,250
through a mobile network.

278
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:49,920
You...

279
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:50,740
There's no need to be surprised.

280
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:52,400
I have a photographic memory.

281
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,140
I think I have

282
00:15:54,350 --> 00:15:55,520
a spare smartphone...

283
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,490
For the time being,

284
00:15:56,490 --> 00:15:57,960
I need to study

285
00:15:58,130 --> 00:15:59,550
how to return to the ancient era.

286
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:00,770
The information I can get online

287
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:01,950
is way more than
what I can get from the library.

288
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:03,380
And, they're updated at a rapid pace.

289
00:16:03,380 --> 00:16:04,430
So, do not bother me

290
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:05,690
for the time being.

291
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:07,940
Logically speaking,

292
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,510
you should be responsible

293
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,390
for providing me with

